title: Flight Simulator 2020 - World Update XVI - Caribbean released!
description:
In this video we will look at the new additions to World Update 16: Caribbean which has been released earlier today. As the name already mentions this WU focuses on a very nice part of the world including the following countries: Antigua, Aruba, Bahamas, Barbados, British Virgin Islands, Cayman Islands, Dominican Republic, Grenada, Haiti, Jamaica, Puerto Rico, Saint Kitts & Nevis, Trinidad & Tobago, Turks & Caicos, and the United States Virgin Islands

In total 7 new handcrafted airports have been added as well as 104 Point of Interest (POI's). Additionally the aerial photographs, satellite data, LIDAR (light detection and ranging) data, DEM (digital elevation model) data, and DTM (digital terrain model) data has been updated.

And as a bonus you will get three Discovery Flights, three Landing Challenges and three Bush Trips.
